data.text:
Silk ties are like the fine worsted wool of the tie realm. They’re versatile and can be worn all 4 seasons. In addition to color and patterns, another distinguishing element to silk ties is whether the pattern is embroidered or printed. Most patterned silk ties have printed patterns. A silk tie with an embroidered pattern is a small way to add a little depth and texture to the overall outfit.

- Italian silk

- Lined construction

- 60" long (152 cm)

- 3.25" wide (8.25 cm)

- Made in Portugal
